Class TravelAdvice

java.lang.Object
com.group8.phase1.gtfs.objects.TravelAdvice
public class TravelAdvice extends Object
A travel advice object for storing information for each trip recommended to the user, containing the shape information for the trip, stop sequence, departure, arrival times, bus number, etc.
